OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1784839668
OL,3,CMan has sentence increased for
OL,4,C'brutal' murder of former partner
OL,6,FA man jailed for the "brutal" murder
OL,7,Fof his former partner in Abingdon in
OL,8,FOxfordshire has had the minimum term
OL,9,Fof his life sentence increased at the
OL,10,FCourt of Appeal.
OL,12,FRobert Richens inflicted more than 60
OL,13,Fblunt force injuries on 40-year-old
OL,14,FRachael Vaughan when he murdered her
OL,15,Fin her home in May 2025, following a
OL,16,Fviolent and controlling relationship.
OL,26,@nD@VOUnD@]O]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/11
