OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1784839668
OL,3,CMan has sentence increased for
OL,4,C'brutal' murder of former partner
OL,6,FHe said: "If the sentence imposed was
OL,7,Flenient, and we submit it was not, it
OL,8,Fwas certainly not unduly lenient."
OL,10,FFollowing the court's ruling, Attorney
OL,11,FGeneral Ellie Reeves said: "Robert
OL,12,FRichens brutally murdered Rachael
OL,13,FVaughan in her own home, the place
OL,14,Fwhere she should have been safest.
OL,16,F"Rachael was subjected to relentlessly
OL,17,Fcontrolling and abusive behaviour. I
OL,18,Fwelcome the Court of Appeal's decision
OL,19,Fto increase Richens' sentence.
OL,26,@nD@JOUpD@bO]sD@\OUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G10/11
